Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.45,0:23:56.78,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1870,540)}蚕食殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.45,0:23:56.78,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(45,540)}だんだん食べる
